        "foot": "MHB 6:1",
        "name": "MHB 6:1",
        "title": "Isaac Watts, 1674 -1748",
        "trans": "\nDOMANKOMA ! Wo sor tsebea\r\nYɛ fɛw dɛ mbrɛ osɛ Nyame:\r\nƆtra wimuwimu n'ekyir noho.\r\nMbrɛ nworaba wɔkɔ aprɔw.",
        "verse": "\nEternal Power, whose high abode\nBecomes the grandeur of a God,\nInfinite lengths beyond the bounds\nWhere stars resolve their little rounds!"
