        "foot": "MHB 6:4",
        "name": "MHB 6:4",
        "title": "Isaac Watts, 1674 -1748",
        "trans": "\nWɔatse Wo nka wɔ ekyirkyir,\r\nMbɔtoaba esua Wo dzin bɔ;\r\nNa Wo nyansaa N'enyimnyam no\r\nMa hen adwen nyina tɔ sin.",
        "verse": "\nEarth from afar has heard Thy fame, \nAnd babes have learnt to lisp Thy name; \nBut O the glories of Thy mind \nLeave all our soaring thoughts behind!"
