        "foot": "MHB 6:5",
        "name": "MHB 6:5",
        "title": "Isaac Watts, 1674 -1748",
        "trans": "\nNyame wo sɔr, nyimpa wɔ ase,\r\nHɛn ndwom nyɛ tsia, na hɛn nsɛm nsuar,\r\nWo ho enyidzi sianka hɛn ndwom,\r\nHɛn ayɛyi ka hɛn anomu.",
        "verse": "\nGod is in heaven, and men below; \nBe short our tunes, our words be few; \nA sacred reverence checks our songs, \nAnd praise sits silent on our tongues."
