        "name": "MHB 7:3",
        "title": "Charles Wesley, 1707-88.",
        "trans": "\nHɛn Egya, hɛn Wura, eyɛ Otumfo,\nW'asɛm a akora hɛn ntsi na yɛrosor yi;\nNdzepa a yenya nyina fi Wo nko hɔ ba,\nHɛn gyirama na hɛn nkwa yɛdze bɔsom Wo.",
        "verse": "\nOur Father and Lord, almighty art Thou; \nPreserved by Thy word, we worship Thee now; \nThe bountiful donor of all we enjoy, \nOur tongues ,to Thine honour, and lives we employ."
