        "foot": "MHB 7:4",
        "name": "MHB 7:4",
        "title": "Charles Wesley, 1707-88.",
        "trans": "\nDza ɔkyen ne nyina, yetow W’ayamuyie.\nAgye wiadze a ayew efi bɔn na yaw m'.\nEdze Wo Ba abɔ werdam apon wiadze,\nDe omfa hen a yetwer No mbra hen sor fie.",
