        "verse": "\nThe earth with its store \r\nOf wonders untold, \r\nAlmighty! Thy power \r\nHath founded of old.\r\nHath stablished it fast \r\nBy a changeless decree, \r\nAnd round it hath cast, \r\nLike a mantle, the sea."
