        "ari": "1:17:1",
        "foot": "MHB 17:1",
        "name": "MHB 17:1",
        "title": "Charles Wesley, 1707-88.",
        "trans": "\nƆSƐ na ɔfata adwontow, \r\nBer na bea biara mu,\r\nEnyimnyam nka hɛn sor Hen,\r\nNokwar na adom Nyame:\r\nHɛn nyina dze ndze dɛɛdɛw\r\nBɔ m' wɔ ndaase kor mu dɛ;\r\nKrɔnkrɔn, krɔnkrɔn, Ewuradze,\r\nAyɛyi nka Wo daa.",
        "verse": "\nMEET and right it is to sing,\n    In every time and place\n    Glory to our heavenly King,\n    The God of truth and grace:\n    Join we then with sweet accord,\n    All in one thanksgiving join:\n    Holy, holy, holy Lord.\n    Eternal praise be Thine."
