        "ari": "1:17:4",
        "foot": "MHB 17:4",
        "name": "MHB 17:4",
        "title": "Charles Wesley, 1707-88.",
        "trans": "\nEgya, yɛkamfo Wo dɔ a\r\nƆmaa Wo Ba n' bowui;\r\nAdom na nokwar, Jesus,\r\nWo na yɛntonton Wo;\r\nSunsum, Ɔwerɛkyekyefo,\r\nObiara nyi Wo ayɛw;\r\nNkpem dɛ yɛbɔtow ndwom,\r\nNa asaase adan ɔsor.   Amen.",
        "verse": "\nFather, God, thy love we praise,\n    Which gave Thy Son to die;\n    Jesus, full of truth and grace.\n    Alike we glorify;\n    Spirit, Comforter divine,\n    Praise by all to thee be given;\n    Till we in full chorus join,\n    And earth is turned to heaven.    Amen."
