        "trans": "\nWo mfe a ɔmmbɔ adze n' no hu a, \r\nDomankoma Ewuradze,\r\nEsunsum wotwa hwe W' enyim\r\nTonton Wo daa nyina.",
        "verse": "\nHow dread are Thine eternal years,  \r\n O everlasting Lord, \r\n By prostrate spirits day and night \r\n Incessantly adored!"
