        "trans": "\nNyansa dɔ! Honam, bɔgya a\r\n'Hwee famu wɔ Adam mu n',\r\nBɛsan nye tamfo no aper,\r\nBɛper edzi konyim.",
        "verse": "\nO wisest love! that flesh and blood \r\n Which did in Adam fail, \r\n Should strive afresh against the foe, \r\n Should strive and should prevail."
