        "foot": "MHB 74:4",
        "name": "MHB 74:4",
        "title": "John Henry Newman, 1801-90.",
        "trans": "\nAkyɛdze kɛse a ɔkyen adom\r\nNtsew honam, bɔgya ho;\r\nNyame ankasa nye No su\r\nNa odzi dɛm dwuma n'.",
        "verse": "\nAnd that a higher gift than grace \r\n Should flesh and blood refine, \r\n God’s Presence, and His very Self \r\n And Essence all-divine."
