        "name": "MHB 77:1",
        "title": "Charles Wesley, 1707-88.",
        "trans": "\nMinsi dɛn mondɔ me Nyame, \r\nMinsi dɛn nyi N' ayɛw?\r\nMinsi dɛn nhu N' adom no war,\r\nNe trɛ, no krɔn, no bun?",
