        "trans": "\nAgyedzifo, hom mbra \r\nDɛw na konyimdzi mu,\r\nHom mbra, O hom nyina mbra Bethlehem;\r\nHom mbra mbɔhwɛ dɛ\r\nWɔawo abɔfo Hen:\r\nO hom mbra mma yɛntonton Ewuradze Christ.",
        "verse": "\nO COME, all ye faithful,\r\nJoyful and triumphant,\r\nCome ye, O come ye to Bethlehem;\r\nCome and behold Him\r\nBorn the King of angels:\r\nO come, let us adore Him, Christ the Lord"
