        "title": "Anonymous, 17th or 18th cent.",
        "trans": "\nNyame mu Nyame, \r\nKan a ofir Kan mu,\r\nHwɛ! oennkyir ɔbaabun n' awotoa;\r\nNyame ara ampa,\r\nWɔwoo N', na wɔannyɛ No;\r\nO hom mbra mma yɛntonton Ewuradze Christ.",
        "verse": "\nTrue God of true God,\r\nLight of light eternal,\r\nLo! He abhors not the virgin’s womb,\r\nSon of the Father,\r\nBegotten, not created :\r\nO come, let us adore Him, Christ the Lord."
