        "foot": "MHB 119:2",
        "name": "MHB 119:2",
        "title": "James Montgomery, 1771-1854.",
        "trans": "\nNguanhwɛfo a hom tsena sar do\r\nRoweɔn hom nguankuw anago,\r\nAfei Nyame nye nyimpa tse,\r\n'Kɔkoaba Ne kan hyerɛn;\r\nHom mbra mbɔsom,\r\nMbɔsom Christ, Ɔhen a wɔawo N'.",
        "verse": "\nShepherds in the fields abiding,\r\nWatching o’er your flocks by night,\r\nGod with man is now residing,\r\nYonder shines the infant Light;\r\nCome and worship, \r\nWorship Christ, the new-born King."
