        "foot": "MHB 119:3",
        "name": "MHB 119:3",
        "title": "James Montgomery, 1771-1854.",
        "trans": "\n'Nyansafo, hom mfi hom dadaw m',\r\nKan fɛɛfɛw bi wɔ ekyir;\r\nHom nhwehwɛ aman apɛdze,\r\nHom ehu N'awoo ho woraba;\r\nHom mbra mbɔsom,\r\nMbɔsom Christ, Ɔhen a wɔawo N'.",
        "verse": "\nSages, leave your contemplation’s, \r\nBrighter visions beam afar; \r\nSeek the great Desire of nations; \r\nYe have seen His natal star; \r\nCome and worship,  \r\nWorship Christ, the new-born King."
