        "ari": "1:175:1",
        "foot": "MHB 175:1",
        "name": "MHB 175:1",
        "title": "Thomas Benson Pollock, 1836-96.",
        "trans": "\nMma nnsu mma Nyia ɔso mbeamudua \r\nDze rokɔ Calvary no;\r\nƆnnserɛ dasanyi ne nyinsu,\r\nƆapen dɛ obowu.",
        "verse": "\nWEEP  not for Him Who onward bears\r\nHis cross to Calvary;\r\nHe does not ask man’s pitying tears,\r\nWho wills for man to die."
