        "ari": "1:175:2",
        "foot": "MHB 175:2",
        "name": "MHB 175:2",
        "title": "Thomas Benson Pollock, 1836-96.",
        "trans": "\nYaw huhu bi a atow N' enyim, \r\nOegura ne nyimpadua n',\r\nMmfir amenhyɛ anaa 'nyimguase:\r\nOnnsuro mbeamudua n'.",
        "verse": "\nThe awful sorrow of His face,\r\nThe bowing of His frame,\r\nCome not from torture or disgrace:\r\nHe fears not cross nor shame."
