        "foot": "MHB 175:3",
        "name": "MHB 175:3",
        "title": "Thomas Benson Pollock, 1836-96.",
        "trans": "\nYaw wenwen a ɔbor do yi, \r\nAhoguan a ɔnnka,\r\nDza Wo dɔ nnya mu ahotɔ yi,\r\nWo nko so ne nyina.",
