        "ari": "1:257:1",
        "foot": "MHB 257:1",
        "name": "MHB 257:1",
        "title": "John Mason Neale, 1818-66.",
        "trans": "\nO bra, O bra Immanuel, \r\nNa bɔpɔn ndɔmmum Israel,\r\nƆka mmɔn ananabea ha\r\nKodu dɛ Nyame Ba bɛba.\r\n \r\nDzi dɛw! Dzi dɛw! Immanuel \r\nBɛba wo nkyɛn, O Israel.",
        "verse": "\n O COME, O come, Immanuel,\r\n And ransom captive Israel, \r\n That mourns in lonely exile here\r\n Until the Son of God appear.\n         Rejoice! Rejoice! Immanuel\r\n         Shall come to thee, O Israel."
