        "name": "MHB 257:3",
        "title": "John Mason Neale, 1818-66.",
        "trans": "\nO bra jesse Poma, bɛgye \r\nWo man fi Satan tum ase;\r\nGye Wo nkorɔfo fi hɛll bun mu,\r\nMa hɔn konyimdzi wɔ wu do.",
        "verse": "\nO come, Thou Rod of Jesse, free\r\nThine own from Satan’s tyranny;\r\n From depths of hell Thy people save,\r\nAnd give them victory over the grave."
