        "trans": "\nBra bɛhyɛ mbérɛwyɛfo dzen;\r\nMa abrɛfo akokodur,\r\nKyérɛ hɛn ma yɛnkasa yie:\r\nSunsum Krͻnkrͻn, tsie hɛn.",
        "verse": "\nCome, to strengthen all the weak;\r\n Give Thy courage to the meek; \r\n Teach our faltering tongues to speak:\r\n Hear us, Holy Spirit."
