        "foot": "MHB 295:9",
        "name": "MHB 295:9",
        "title": "Thomas Benson Pollock, 1836-96;",
        "trans": "\nFa hɛn fa kwan tseabaa n’ mu.\r\nSɛ yɛfom a, bͻ hɛn kͻkͻ;\r\nYɛbͻ mpaa a, serɛ ma hɛn.\r\nSunsum Krͻnkrͻn, tsie hɛn.",
        "verse": "\nKeep  us in the narrow way;\r\n Warn us when we go astray; \r\n Plead within us when we pray:\r\n Hear us, Holy Spirit."
