        "foot": "MHB 338:4",
        "name": "MHB 338:4",
        "title": "Frances Jane van Alstyne, 1830-1915.",
        "trans": "\nPer gye hɔn a wɔreyew: \r\nDwuma 'i da wo do;\r\nEwuradze bɛma w' ho ahoɔdzen.\r\nFrɛ hɔn ma wɔnsan mbra,\r\nFa abotar twe hɔn;\r\nSe kobɔfo n' dɛ Gyefo n' wui maa no.",
        "verse": "\nRescue the perishing-Duty demands it;\r\nStrength for thy labour the Lord will provide;\r\nBack to the narrow way, Patiently win them;\r\nTell the poor wanderer a Saviour has died."
