        "ari": "1:517:2",
        "foot": "MHB 517:2",
        "name": "MHB 517:2",
        "title": "Edgar Page Stites, b. 1837.",
        "trans": "\nMber rutwa m' kɔ a motwer No,\r\nNda resen yi, motwer No,\r\nDza obesi bia 'a motwer No,\r\nMotwer Jesus, noara nye n'.",
        "verse": "\nBrightly doth His Spirit shine\r\nInto this poor heart of mine: \r\nWhile He leads I cannot fall, \r\nTrusting Jesus, that is all."
