        "ari": "1:519:2",
        "foot": "MHB 519:2",
        "name": "MHB 519:2",
        "title": "Charles Wesley, 1707-88.",
        "trans": "\nWo tum wɔ nyimpa mberɛwyɛ mu\r\nBɛyɛ hɛn nyina kor;\r\nW'enyim a ɔkyerɛ hɛn kwan ntsi\r\nYɛnantsew gya mu sɔnn.",
        "verse": "\nThy power, in human weakness shown,\r\nShall make us all entire;\r\nWe now Thy guardian presence own,\r\nAnd walk unburned in fire."
