        "title": "Charles Wesley, 1707-88.",
        "trans": "\nNyimpa Ba, gyedzi mu yehu W',\r\nYetuw W'akwankyerɛ ho;\r\nAbɔ hɛn ho aprɔw ehyia yi,\r\nYetum gyina ogya mu.",
        "verse": "\nThee, Son of Man, by faith we see,\r\nAnd glory in our Guide;\r\nSurrounded and upheld by Thee,\r\nThe fiery test abide."
