        "foot": "MHB 520:2",
        "name": "MHB 520:2",
        "title": "Frances Ridley Havergal, 1836-79.",
        "trans": "\nMedze m'akoma brɛ Wo, \r\n'Koma a minnyim mu nsɛm;\r\nKɔhwinyi, kobɔnyi n',\r\nAkoma bɔn ampa.\r\nM'Agyenkwa, medze hyɛ Wo nsa\r\nMa m'akoma nsi pi mma Wo.",
        "verse": "\nMy heart to Thee I bring, \r\nThe heart I cannot read;\r\nA faithless, wandering thing, \r\nAn evil heart indeed. \r\nI bring it, Saviour, now to Thee,\r\nThat fixed and faithful it may be."
