        "foot": "MHB 520:5",
        "name": "MHB 520:5",
        "title": "Frances Ridley Havergal, 1836-79.",
        "trans": "\nMedze me dɛw brɛ Wo, \r\nDɛw a Wo dɔ dze ana m',\r\nDɛ memfa nyɛ atwer a \r\nMofow mipinkyɛn Wo.\r\nGyefo, Woara tɔɔ ne nyina maa m';\r\nMedze ne nyina gu W'enyim.",
        "verse": "\nMy joys to Thee I bring,\r\nThe joys Thy love hath given,\r\nThat each may be a wing.\r\nTo lift me nearer heaven.\r\nI bring them, Saviour, all to Thee;\r\nFor Thou hast purchased all for me."
