        "foot": "MHB 520:6",
        "name": "MHB 520:6",
        "title": "Frances Ridley Havergal, 1836-79.",
        "trans": "\nMedze mo nkwa brɛ Wo, \r\nMennda ho nndze moho;\r\nGyefo, ma menya Wodze,\r\nWo nko Wodze daa nyina.\r\nM'akoma, mo nkwa, m'adze nyina,\r\nMedze brɛ Wo, me Hen, Gyefo.",
        "verse": "\nMy life I bring to Thee,\r\nI would not be my own;\r\nO Saviour, let me be\r\nThine ever, Thine alone,\r\nMy heart, my life, my all I bring\r\nTo Thee, my Saviour and my King."
