        "foot": "MHB 521:1",
        "name": "MHB 521:1",
        "title": "Frances Ridley Havergal, 1836-79.",
        "trans": "\nMOTWER Wo, Ewuradze Jesus,\r\nMotwer Wo nkotoo,\r\nMotwer Wo ma meenya nkwagye \r\nKɛse kwa.",
