        "name": "MHB 521:2",
        "title": "Frances Ridley Havergal, 1836-79.",
        "trans": "\nMotwer Wo kotow W'ananadze\r\nSerɛ bɔnfakyɛ;\r\nW'adom nye ehumbɔbɔr kɛse n'\r\nNa motwer.",
