        "foot": "MHB 521:3",
        "name": "MHB 521:3",
        "title": "Frances Ridley Havergal, 1836-79.",
        "trans": "\nMotwer Wo ma aatsew mo ho\r\nWɔ bɔgya bura n' mu;\r\nMotwer Wo ma aayɛ m' krɔnkrɔn,\r\nWo bɔgyaa m'.",
        "verse": "\nI am trusting Thee for cleansing\r\nIn the crimson flood;\r\nTrusting Thee to make me holy \r\n\tBy Thy blood"
