        "foot": "MHB 521:5",
        "name": "MHB 521:5",
        "title": "Frances Ridley Havergal, 1836-79.",
        "trans": "\nMotwer Wo ama meenya tum,\r\nIrinngyaa me da;\r\nNsɛm a Woara dze bɛma me n'\r\nBedzi nyim.",
