        "ari": "1:655:1",
        "foot": "MHB 655:1",
        "name": "MHB 655:1",
        "title": "F.B.P., 16th or 17th cent.",
        "trans": "\nJERUSALEM, m'ahomka fie!\r\nM'bɛba wo hɔ dabɛn?\r\nM'awerɛhow bɔbɔ adze dabɛn?\r\nDabɛn na m'bohu",
        "verse": "\n0. There Magdalene hath left her moan,\r\nAnd cheerfully doth sing\r\nWith blessèd saints, whose harmony\r\nIn every street doth ring."
